&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Salaried GP Vacancy at Central Healthcare, Scarborough&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Central Healthcare are looking for interested GPs to work with us in our Scarborough Town Centre practice.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;This is a really exciting time for Central Healthcare and this vacancy would suit a GP who is willing to embrace change and thrives on innovation &amp; challenge, including the immense potential for innovation. Having recently formed a new partnership with Haxby Group, who are rated ‘outstanding’ by the CQC; there is immense scope of progression for the right candidate. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Both Haxby Group and Central Healthcare are accredited training practices and by joining forces we are able to strengthen staff training and development opportunities for all of our staff. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;We encourage efficient working practices such as telephone / video consultations, electronic prescribing, using online workflow and developing innovative care plans for health management &amp; improvement. GPs have the opportunity to provide supervision and support to the wide range of healthcare professionals and trainees working within our Practice. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Further benefits that Central Healthcare can offer are: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible working practices, including the ability to work from home when suitable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support from a larger clinical team, including senior GPs, primary care practitioners and specialist advanced nurse practitioners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A state-of-the-art digital patient access and consultation system and appointment booking to improve waiting times and availability of appointments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Investment in new IT and telephone infrastructure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support from a large HR, Finance and Business Intelligence team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help with patient communications and engagement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexibility of staffing as specialists can be available from across sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Benefit from the experience and knowledge embedded in a practice that has achieved outstanding results in areas with a similar patient population.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunities to develop special interests&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support from Haxby Group Training, which provides education to a wide range of primary care clinicians&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To arrange a visit or for an informal discussion please contact: Joanna.dodds@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
